name: Princess Oneil
description: very simple lady who need love and to be care for, l am a very humble type and respectfull. l love going out and love meeting people. l relate with everybody, l don’t descriminate, l believe everybody are the same and that we are one family. l hate lies and l love when people are honest. l love kids a lot. l love been with them. l forgive people easily, l don’t get angry unneccesarily. l am always happy at any given condition or situation, l have fear of God and l take things of God very seriously.
